name: I Want To Leave
description:
Made for Nokia 3310 Jam 4

Overworked and underpaid, you are wrapping up an Earth recon mission when you receive last-minute orders to begin the Great Harvest. Get those humans into the mothership above!

With a variety of tools at your disposal, the method is up to you. Will you carefully deliver your specimens intact, or wreak total havoc and beam up the giblets? As you progress, you can build interactive systems that automate your labor. Why not make your life easier, and pocket the difference?

Best get cracking—your skinflint commander doesn't pay overtime!

A game by Yossarian, Bokonon, and Turgidharrier

CONTROLS

WASD / Arrows / Numpad 8426 — Move

Spacebar / Numpad 5 — Use Tool / Confirm

QE / Numpad 79 — Cycle Tool

Tab / Numpad 0 — Enter / Exit Shop
